cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DB

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on learning distributed representations of entities and documents from a knowledge base, which is a natural language processing task. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a likely category as the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed model on text classification tasks. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper describes a neural network model for representation learning. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with learning representations of entities and documents, which is a fundamental problem in AI. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with knowledge bases and their descriptions.
